snippet.title: Squadron II - Official Teaser [HD]
snippet.description:
After the victory of the intergalactic coalition, the alliances have been shattered. The alien waves of the Overmind bent the Orion Guild and took possession of it's forges. The construction of their metaships has been multiplied by millions. That's why Orion Guild needs new experienced pilots, to overcome the alien threat. Be part of the Team Squadron and save our future!

Follow the updates on this amazing shoot'em up here :
